<br>
Faction correlates well to sociability but not all mobs with no faction are asocial. OOT parrots are social but have no faction, Specs are social but have no faction, etc. I don't know of any ones that have faction that are not social, but a number without faction are.<br>
<br>
Try or ask.<br>
<br>
I can tell you Cougars in EW are NOT. _Savage_ dire wolves in EW are NOT.<br>
